  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl210_LabelType\">You are familiar with the flora of your native forest and have rudimentary skill as an herbalist.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl210_LabelType\">Green-Scaled Kobold Heritage</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl210_LabelType\">Once per day, you can attempt a DC 20 Survival check instead of a Craft (alchemy) check to create a single dose of scent cloak (<em>Ultimate Equipment</em> 105) without paying any cost for raw materials. Any scent cloak created using this method must be used within 24 hours, or it becomes inert.</span></p>",
